    "description": "Borosil Global Group is actively seeking a talented and motivated Store Manager to join our dynamic team in Vadodara. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Borosil Global Group:\nBorosil Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Loyalty Programs\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Learning & development budget\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Borosil Global Group!",
